{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d2890fa4643bd49c152a2554",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一粒小种子：旺加里·马塔伊的故事",
        "text_hash": "2e20dea207aa93c687a02b3c330f876f5716c426f4d41f557cd6573e13074135",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_879d066ff29b535fb0e2bead",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里和她的母亲在田野里手牵着手。",
        "text_hash": "5fa1fffb5a3157a2d70f25ed9149ae30517a7ed3b6fbbc2c4adb4be8f63663fc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_93e36033fdaa206b33dd8f82",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在东非肯尼亚山山坡上的一个村庄里，一个小女孩和母亲一起在田里劳作。她的名字叫旺加里。",
        "text_hash": "16f1aaa5f5764e90dc66454ba85e8c2feac97918760f1157952445a02c5a4aff",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a80ff3fdc33bc9567d483573",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里把蔬菜种子播进泥土里。",
        "text_hash": "04d7fe1f749f42249b2586e8a50f388f581639ba67b830775cb8fbee8d905c98",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_aeea9aef9eb20647208aff54",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里喜欢待在户外。在家里的菜园中，她用砍刀把土块打碎。她把小小的种子按进温暖的泥土里。",
        "text_hash": "6db76e44acc7c7df54ce49803fa2f74257ff70f73b0070ff194f9518c80bab5f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_92b598cb162f0a5a763b8ea9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "天色渐暗。旺加里把她的蔬菜带回家。",
        "text_hash": "5085355d4a630c9b989073d41f4b96142b64e1dc50b8c8be47bfc731d41bf1ff",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9dc702f9f5d68731ef44617e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她一天中最喜欢的时刻是日落之后不久。当天色暗到看不清植物时，旺加里就知道该回家了。",
        "text_hash": "616aa5cc92bd20a5ecb84be3f5ebaad9d77b20c105e9c76c7e5ab41c51bf2402",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_22102ac6031e907856b9ade3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她会沿着田间狭窄的小路走，一路上穿过河流。",
        "text_hash": "2debe962f003a3e767de0f7dd1b5e568d25a228a30f32d858d9c414c1492bdc6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3d457bb7c7af8e7f2874dce3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里和她的哥哥把她的书包带去学校。",
        "text_hash": "dab81dc36d36582f50ed25b45c930c31ca28c5491a6b99dce34087e2fa498a96",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dc6e0ea5f438361d716348c8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里是个聪明的孩子，迫不及待想去上学。但是她的父母希望她留下来，在家帮忙。",
        "text_hash": "2cde26b0d532298853e7ad37ae51d7ac506f7863e1b8a806c625729b9e88fbb9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_82d490627ea2a89faa518f00",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她七岁时，她的哥哥说服父母让她去上学。",
        "text_hash": "e6e957b2575eff5967a830c2938350f41c7b3d4254716a7dd5e3a0a15a723847",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_abaca8d94671ff4c7bed1d1f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一本画着各大洲图案的练习本摊开放在桌子上。",
        "text_hash": "a1f6e2b255b7da425efd0040d2db5d5a4f3337b4634d44a54c3add5415a8acae",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ff95beb7f8bfc1556be20032",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她喜欢学习！",
        "text_hash": "283cc955eabaada17241a59615293ee88762e70f499266825c497a937edc87b7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_54611d14318237cb47838d1a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里每读一本书，就学到越来越多的知识。",
        "text_hash": "86d5e104ed5a5db2d39689beb12b6e516af2397a782ef02e14875222a4c2ee44",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_79d2da49e999335ac3fe75f2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她在学校表现非常出色，因此受邀去美利坚合众国学习。",
        "text_hash": "4933789899c5533d76a50305b1b05810894289d8a39c330fafc890a616a20c12",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2d6a3c2ac674b943b2b7bcd3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里很兴奋！她想更多地了解这个世界。",
        "text_hash": "a482f6691f75642ec192bb4fb8a96108aa1e97dae28e05b924f36e6d02f5438b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5cf5b22b66dddb505aeba142",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一只放大镜举在一朵黄色花朵上方。",
        "text_hash": "9298f77b2a1a09a87f06cd2abfa76824657ad40601c96b73ca20de5cb4d71574",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b63cb91ff48dce4f30866cd9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在美国的大学里，旺加里学到了许多新东西。她研究植物以及它们如何生长。她也想起了自己是怎样长大的：在美丽的肯尼亚森林里，在树荫下和兄弟们一起玩游戏。",
        "text_hash": "7c1194c63d78c752352c01932c08ba9918e5719cac432a05777116ace9175db1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f47599d2d614f946f700775a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里坐在一堆书上读书。",
        "text_hash": "05786cd0927a4e83d5766a7db806b14633624dc80f3aa89fa1f900206dc88a5d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_37d3188ae96b5e77428e3b87",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她学得越多，就越意识到自己热爱肯尼亚人民。她希望他们幸福而自由。她学得越多，就越想起她在非洲的家。",
        "text_hash": "670dc9167635b7d18dd7a07a1a5470b1bfbe3ae1de2acc9a44647ae8346824ea",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ebf614513d537a2fdf2e4d8b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一只雄鹿独自站在荒芜的田野里。",
        "text_hash": "28de0821ae4d904be4159a4e54b096494c7c8fef6ee4c6c9ebdc2047eb1a7e33",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_af6f6059885642bf32ab74d6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "完成学业后，她回到了肯尼亚。但是她的国家已经变了。巨大的农场在土地上绵延展开。",
        "text_hash": "9f10df888d9bc98540642fe2897e925e71c2bfa264a536ce224ba04cb28bdad9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3ba780901836f721f87236ca",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "妇女们没有木柴来生火做饭。人们很贫穷，孩子们挨着饿。",
        "text_hash": "35e9d94a2ed9832bb0b45a5b9c9b615c7dd11ada7861a37d8f2e666086f353a5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7b9c391ed2f614232f22ef15",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里教一位年长的妇女如何在泥土里种植。",
        "text_hash": "17e3be112c701dc15ed6b1ea6daf84fbb8b0966648620956d65ed93466fe3995",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dee6922533d26c2a6e58ad5e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里知道该怎么做。她教妇女们如何用种子种树。",
        "text_hash": "57728d152fc6954029e84ba17540aa41b2743144a4d90c5686b5b7a9d225fbb8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4ac744f1b91d73e3c2fb4ef2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "妇女们卖掉树苗，用赚来的钱照顾家人。",
        "text_hash": "4c36e4fdbf4f94d642c19c3f8f981ece7b959dd00976ffbbcb753655bcbfdde3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a596443f17368cf19e998ebb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "妇女们非常高兴。旺加里帮助她们感到自己有力量、很坚强。",
        "text_hash": "182cf63cb5381988d78d5230439c1382ab6cc6bd1f6096ff64d8e360af88d93e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_428e9c4e94dd62eb9b0d7eea",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小树苗长成了一片片树林。",
        "text_hash": "55e593941f308a2c20039148c1b7b8568534e9491105d88bb349615aa59f852a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5d3d26136eb5224b48c597f8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "随着时间流逝，新栽的树长成了森林，河流也重新开始流淌。旺加里的理念传遍了非洲。",
        "text_hash": "c4ca29799737f158451d51b40abbf8dbd3d9e3ad1235afcef1b68cd0949aa7c0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8580b3dc4d05b364da511486",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "如今，数百万棵树从旺加里的种子中生长起来。",
        "text_hash": "d9ec05ad6bc9615a4a9c39ddea90523acaa56c48f13a7a175526d5015b502f4b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c38c0f05a5bb00b140f6148e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一幅旺加里的肖像被树木环绕，她戴着肯尼亚头饰。",
        "text_hash": "25e9da76eba8b970b54ed7afae9d16c32f29892b5d0494cec89d31c44737129f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b7d1641da76a512f4b93e995",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里一直努力工作。全世界的人都注意到了她，并授予她一个著名奖项。这个奖项叫诺贝尔和平奖，她是第一位获得该奖的非洲女性。",
        "text_hash": "461636aca3695fcc1a6cd5d7628720aa1a9acdb799cb9783265978136449a0fd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_db9995d5b96d0d20fb74c0dd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一棵美丽的老树高高地、自豪地挺立在田野里。",
        "text_hash": "28d06c01b36b4e4348b24f77257f38ff27b4c504544af5952777b169cbff7cf4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1663b70e67bc7955658576b7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "旺加里于2011年去世，但每当我们看到一棵美丽的树时，都可以想起她。",
        "text_hash": "2927e4361acf56b244217361449fdc325a78f3d185e4bf1acc0d067f008fc025",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_df4d6403fff695c0cdef265c"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
